title: Suggestion: Add Image Captioning Model Example for Android
body_html:
This is a suggestion to add Android example for our deep-learning based tensorflow-android app which captions live camera frames in real-time.
https://github.com/neural-nuts/Cam2Caption

This app uses pre-trained model generated using
https://github.com/neural-nuts/image-caption-generator
